title: Lul wut

replies.body: To be slightly fair, while it definitely looks like fizz it does also look different at the same time, and it's not like fizz's look is 100% original in the first place (basically a fish with legs) and while Fizz does have a trident, if you look the third point isn't in the middle of the two, but actually in a circle, whereas this is more of a traditional Trident.
Yeah many of them use direct screen shots from LOL as advertising for games that are nothing like it.
